    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🥚 Eggtastic</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Eggtastic</strong> is a creative puzzle game with a retro twist. Your goal is simple: take a blank egg and transform it to match the target design. Use paints, masks, and clever layering to crack each challenge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From simple splashes of color to tricky combinations of stripes, stickers, and patterns, every level pushes your creativity and logic just a little further.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎨 <strong>Core Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Paint &amp; Mask</strong> – Combine ink, cover, and design your egg to match the goal exactly.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Retro Style</strong> – Pixel-inspired visuals and classic puzzle mechanics.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Seasonal Levels</strong> – Special Halloween and Christmas puzzles keep the fun festive.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>For Everyone</strong> – Easy to learn, and fun for all ages.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you’re looking for a quick puzzle break or a relaxing design challenge, <i>Eggtastic</i> delivers colorful fun one egg at a time.</p>",
